---
// SlicedLabs · legal · © 2026 SlicedLabs — Shipping Policy
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
const updated = "June 22, 2026";
---
<Base title="Shipping Policy — SlicedLabs" description="How and when SlicedLabs merchandise ships.">
  <section class="wrap" style="max-width:46rem; padding-block:clamp(2.5rem,7vw,4rem);">
    <p class="mono" data-reveal>legal</p>
    <h1 data-reveal style="--i:1; font-size:clamp(2rem,6vw,3.4rem); margin:.3rem 0 0;"><span class="blend-text">Shipping Policy</span></h1>
    <hr class="blade" data-reveal style="--i:2; max-width:10rem; margin:1.2rem 0 1.2rem;" />
    <p class="mono" style="color:var(--muted); margin:0 0 1.4rem;">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    <div class="glass island" data-reveal style="margin-bottom:1.6rem;">
      <p style="margin:0; color:var(--muted);"><strong style="color:var(--ink);">A note.</strong> This is a good-faith starting template — not legal advice. Have a qualified attorney review it before you rely on it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="prose" data-reveal>
      <p>Merchandise is made to order and shipped by our print-on-demand partner (Printful). Digital products and memberships are delivered instantly to your account — no shipping involved.</p>

      <h2>Processing &amp; transit</h2>
      <p>Most orders are produced in <strong>2–5 business days</strong>, then ship. US delivery typically takes <strong>3–7 business days</strong> after that. Busy seasons can add time.</p>

      <h2>Where we ship</h2>
      <p>We currently ship within the United States. Shipping cost (if any) is shown at checkout; we may offer free shipping over a threshold.</p>

      <h2>Tracking</h2>
      <p>When your order ships, we email a tracking link, and you can always check status from your <a href="/account">account</a>.</p>

      <h2>Problems &amp; lost packages</h2>
      <p>If a package is lost or arrives damaged, contact us within <strong>30 days</strong> of the expected delivery and we'll make it right — see the <a href="/refunds">Refund Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Shipping questions? Reach us via the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
